    "summary": "The user, expressing concern about hypoglycemia due to low food intake, repeatedly asks if it is safe to skip their basal insulin dose. The assistant consistently refuses to allow the user to skip the dose, providing physiological justifications and recommending small snacks to mitigate the risk of a crash.",
